The paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as word relatedness and named-entity disambiguation, which are typically studied in the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The use of the Wikipedia hyperlink graph also suggests a possible connection to Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
